The '''Outland Regions''' was a vast area of [[Realspace/Legends|space]] in the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim Territories]] of [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]], including the space around the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Eriadu/Legends|Eriadu]].

In the last decades of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]], the Outland Regions were patrolled by the [[Warship/Legends|warships]] of the [[Outland Regions Security Force/Legends|Republic Outland Regions Security Force]], and under the Galactic Empire, [[Grand Moff/Legends|Grand Moff]] [[Wilhuff Tarkin/Legends|Wilhuff Tarkin]] of [[Oversector Outer]] could have been styled as [[Governor/Legends|Governor]] of the Imperial Outland Regions.

